@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sxvuxj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.45 * v1 + 0.48)) * ((v1 + 0.30 * tmp + 0.54) + (v1 + 0.14 - tmp + 0.96)))
    tmp = wp.abs((0.36 * (v0 + 0.36 - tmp + 0.55)))
    v2 = (v1 + wp.exp((v1 + 0.59 - v0 + 0.42)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.cos(v2 + 0.69) * (tmp + 0.95 + v2 + 0.64)))
    data[tid] = v0
